OL,3,CPCC defends handling of chief
OL,4,Cconstable misconduct complaints
OL,6,FDevon and Cornwall's Police and Crime
OL,7,FCommissioner has defended her handling
OL,8,Fof misconduct complaints against two
OL,9,Fchief constables, insisting she is
OL,10,Fstill the right person to hold the
OL,11,Fforce to account.
OL,13,FAlison Hernandez denied she has
OL,14,Foverseen a period of chaos, and blamed
OL,15,Fthe police watchdog for "unfortunate"
OL,16,Fdelays in resolving disciplinary
OL,17,Fissues.
