OL,3,CPCC defends handling of chief
OL,4,Cconstable misconduct complaints
OL,6,FDevon and Cornwall Police's former
OL,7,FChief Constable Will Kerr was
OL,8,Fsuspended in 2023, after it emerged he
OL,9,Fwas under investigation over
OL,10,Fallegations of sexual offences during
OL,11,Fhis work with the Police Service of
OL,12,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,14,FActing Chief Constable Jim Colwell was
OL,15,Fthen suspended in November after
OL,16,Fallegations of misconduct. He has
OL,17,Fsince returned to his role as Deputy
OL,18,FChief Constable with a written warning
OL,19,F"to last for 18 months" after
OL,20,Fmisconduct was proven by a police
OL,21,Fwatchdog panel.
