OL,3,CPCC defends handling of chief
OL,4,Cconstable misconduct complaints
OL,6,FThe force is currently being led by
OL,7,Finterim Chief Constable James Vaughan.
OL,9,FEarlier this week, having seen the
OL,10,Fcriminal investigation against him
OL,11,Fdropped, but with a police watchdog
OL,12,Finquiry still ongoing, Mr Kerr
OL,13,Fannounced his retirement.
OL,15,FIt means the force is now looking for
OL,16,Fits fourth leader in fewer than two
OL,17,Fyears.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
