OL,3,CPCC defends handling of chief
OL,4,Cconstable misconduct complaints
OL,6,FHernandez said: "As a Police and Crime
OL,7,FCommissioner, if any information comes
OL,8,Fin about potential misconduct, you
OL,9,Frefer it to the Independent Office for
OL,10,FPolice Conduct," she said.
OL,12,F"Then it's out of your control. There
OL,13,Fare procedures and processes you must
OL,14,Ffollow. It's just unfortunate that it
OL,15,Ftakes so long to carry out any form of
OL,16,Finvestigation."
OL,18,F'We are stable right now'
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
