OL,3,CPCC defends handling of chief
OL,4,Cconstable misconduct complaints
OL,6,FShe added: "Fundamentally, the
OL,7,Fstandards start with me. I set the
OL,8,Ftone by employing the right or wrong
OL,9,Fchief constable.
OL,11,F'Will (Kerr) has not been found guilty
OL,12,Fof anything yet. It's just sad that
OL,13,Fwe've had these difficult and
OL,14,Foverlapping investigations.
OL,16,F"But we are stable right now, James
OL,17,FVaughan is doing an excellent job and
OL,18,Fhe is the Chief Constable as we speak."
OL,20,FMs Hernandez said she believes the
OL,21,Fpolice watchdog is not fit for purpose.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
