OL,3,CPCC defends handling of chief
OL,4,Cconstable misconduct complaints
OL,6,F"The problem we've got, is that they
OL,7,Fneed to give Police and Crime
OL,8,FCommissioners more power to take
OL,9,Fcontrol of these situations, instead
OL,10,Fof allowing third parties that haven't
OL,11,Fgot the people of Devon and Cornwall
OL,12,Fat their heart," she said.
OL,14,F"I would have liked to have
OL,15,Fcommissioned my own investigation to
OL,16,Fdecide what those timescales needed to
OL,17,Flook like. It certainly would have
OL,18,Fbeen done a lot quicker."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
