OL,3,CPCC defends handling of chief
OL,4,Cconstable misconduct complaints
OL,6,FSteve Race, Labour MP for Exeter, said
OL,7,Fthe whole saga does not reflect well
OL,8,Fon the region.
OL,10,F"This has been a really bad period for
OL,11,Fthe police force," he said.
OL,13,F"I really want the commissioner to
OL,14,Fdraw a line under this, to recruit the
OL,15,Fnext chief constable who we can be
OL,16,Fconfident can turn the force around."
